  Group Performance Dashboard - Track Multiple Assets with RS Rating & Returns

  Visual table dashboard displaying performance metrics for predefined asset groups. Monitor main indexes, sectors, commodities, bonds, and industry groups side-by-side.

  Features:
  - 25+ pre-configured groups (Main Indexes, SPY Sectors, Finance, Healthcare, etc.)
  - RS Rating (1-99 strength vs benchmark) or % Return metrics
  - Customizable timeframes (Year, YTD, Quarter, Custom periods)
  - Sortable performance columns
  - Color-coded cells (green/gray/red for quick analysis)
  - Adjustable table position and size

  Two versions available:
  - v1: Supports both RS Rating and % Return modes (best for small-medium groups)
  - v3: RS Rating only, optimized for large groups up to 39 items

  Perfect for sector rotation, relative strength analysis, and multi-asset monitoring.

